    <item>
      <title>On this Sunday’s episode of @messylunchshow, our hosts @gizzierskine and @leonie...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DWYanqvggAq/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DWYanqvggAq/"><img src="https://scontent-lhr6-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/656221232_18576608176055140_5584643801245499958_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s640x640_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=102&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg2MTk1Mzc1NTYzMzI4NzIxMDE4NTc2NjA4MTY3MDU1MTQw.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwODB4MTkyMC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=tN5vKLVzOz0Q7kNvwHz-WMw&amp;_nc_oc=AdoKPPUk8mJoxyT5a5_I92Q7DyW5H9UzVCjc_hQUkpNsvlQTcTiWbnRvXS1GNPT1kus&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-lhr6-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=r1OsHscDa2Ng3QTQW75Yig&amp;_nc_ss=7a3ba&amp;oh=00_Af1t9AwKIFWUU2fBEbkjfbI6HIU62X9hUp_ivuVA13QuHg&amp;oe=69D6D7FD" alt="Video-thumbnail fra @baxterdury" /></a></p><p><strong>🎬 Video</strong></p><p><strong>@baxterdury</strong></p><p>On this Sunday’s episode of @messylunchshow, our hosts @gizzierskine and @leoniemaycooper have @baxterdury , the “Nylon Panther”, the “Sausage man” and the UK’s answer to Serge Gainsbourg, and take him to the infamous @ottos_restaurant , where we see some fever dream like scenarios play out at the hands of the flambe and duck press master, Otto Tepasse who is a legend in his own right. We have levelled up the chaos and it’s hysterical. We cant wait for you to see this one!<br/>
<br/>
It’s your bi-monthly calling to head over to the channel and subscribe for all the added extras. If you’re already on board, we will see you Sunday. Brace yourself. This episode is EVERYTHING we wanted to achieve with the show. <br/>
